When JasonVanJason, the greatest Smithy to ever live, created this weapon, he conceived it with a smirk upon his grill, knowing this would be his greatest work yet;the chaos it would bring... However, he seemed to manifest this chaos a little too effectively as a stream of gluttenous saliva poured from his now grinning face, short circuiting many components on it, but knowing his genius, allowed the failed work into circulation regardless, knowing some day an apprentice Printer would come to appreciate it.
